HEADWORD: Chlorometer
<hw>Chlo*rom"e*ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>chlorom⟦egrave⟧tre</ets>. See <er>Chlorine</er>, and
<er>-meter</er>.]</ety> <def>An instrument to test the decoloring or
bleaching power of chloride of lime.</def>⟦br⟧
